  "text": "Let us first compare our new scheme with the basic probabilistic scheme [CITATION_1] and the q-composite scheme [CITATION_2] ]. Figure 7 compares the fraction of compromised direct keys shared between noncompromised sensor nodes given the same p, m, and storage overhead. We can see that our scheme performs significantly better than the other two schemes. It also shows that the more precise the sensor deployment is, the higher security it can guarantee.",
